OL,3,CInvestigation by regulator into PM Law
OL,4,CLtd
OL,6,FAn investigation into a "potential
OL,7,Ffraud" has been launched by the
OL,8,FSolicitors Regulation Authority (SRA)
OL,9,Ffollowing the unexpected closure of PM
OL,10,FLaw Ltd.
OL,12,FThe Sheffield-based company operated
OL,13,Facross the country including
OL,14,FButterworths Solicitors which had four
OL,15,Fbranches in Cumbria.
OL,17,FThe firm shut suddenly on Monday 2
OL,18,FFebruary which has led to the SRA
OL,19,Finvestigation.
