OL,3,CInvestigation by regulator into PM Law
OL,4,CLtd
OL,6,FJonathan Peddie, Executive Director of
OL,7,FLegal and Enforcement, said: "We are
OL,8,Finvestigating a potential fraud,
OL,9,Fincluding the misappropriation of
OL,10,Fclient money.
OL,12,F"We recognise that there is a strong
OL,13,Fpublic interest in this case, given
OL,14,Fthe significant impact on clients.
OL,15,FAlongside doing everything we can to
OL,16,Fprotect and support clients, we are
OL,17,Fmoving as quickly as we can with our
OL,18,Finvestigation. It is a complex
OL,19,Fpicture, and we are still establishing
OL,20,Fthe core facts.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
