OL,3,CInvestigation by regulator into PM Law
OL,4,CLtd
OL,6,F"We are focused on establishing what
OL,7,Foccurred, how it happened, and who was
OL,8,Fresponsible. We will take appropriate
OL,9,Faction to protect the public,
OL,10,Fincluding enforcement action against
OL,11,Fanyone who has been involved in
OL,12,Fmisconduct.
OL,14,F"We have also shared information with
OL,15,Fthe appropriate law enforcement
OL,16,Fagencies."
OL,18,FThe SRA said that they immediately
OL,19,Flaunched an investigation into PM Law
OL,20,FLtd, connected individuals and
OL,21,Fintervened into the firm on 4 February.
