OL,3,CInvestigation by regulator into PM Law
OL,4,CLtd
OL,6,FIn a statement the SRA said: "Our
OL,7,Fintervention agent, Gordons LLP, has
OL,8,Ftaken possession of all files and
OL,9,Fmoney (including client funds) held by
OL,10,Fthe firm.
OL,12,F"We have provided information and
OL,13,Fsupport to clients who are impacted
OL,14,Fand our agent is diligently working
OL,15,Fthrough tens of thousands of files to
OL,16,Fidentify and contact everyone impacted.
OL,18,F"The live nature of the investigation
OL,19,Fmeans that we will not provide further
OL,20,Fcomment on this case at this stage."
